WEBVTT

00:07:59.400 --> 00:08:00.600
But we have them,

00:08:01.280 --> 00:08:05.480
and we pay for them in lives cut short.

00:08:06.320 --> 00:08:08.976
That's why sounding the alarm

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:13.776
about the impact of racism on health
in the United States,

00:08:13.800 --> 00:08:18.096
the ongoing institutional
and interpersonal violence

00:08:18.120 --> 00:08:20.096
that people of color face,

00:08:20.120 --> 00:08:24.456
compounded by our tragic legacy

00:08:24.480 --> 00:08:27.400
of 250 years of slavery,

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:30.240
90 years of Jim Crow